title: BBQ Burnt Trends 12/4: Jay-Z, Euphoria, WEED, LL Cool J
itunes:title: BBQ Burnt Trends 12/4: Jay-Z, Euphoria, WEED, LL Cool J
description:
On this edition of BBQ Burnt Trends Jack and Miles discuss today being Jay-Z's 51st birthday, Euphoria dropping a 2-part holiday special, the MORE act passes the House more or less along party lines, and Twitter is recounting the tale of LL Cool J wearing a FUBU hat during a GAP commercial.
